1. One or more non-transitory computer-readable media storing executable instructions that, when executed by one or more processors, cause the one or more processors to perform operations comprising:
receiving a request to notify users associated with an impact area where an event is estimated to impact, the event including at least one of a hurricane, a tornado, a fire, a flood, or an earthquake;
retrieving first policy data for a first user and second policy data for a second user, the first policy data including information about an insurance policy for the first user and the second policy data including information about an insurance policy for the second user;
